</h2>
<h3>
    Columbia River Tributaries
</h3>
<p>
    The Columbia River and its tributaries are prime pink salmon territory. Focus on areas near the confluence with the Willamette River and further upstream.
</p>
<h3>
    Sandy River Hotspots
</h3>
<p>
    One of the most accessible pink salmon rivers near Portland, the <strong>Sandy River</strong> offers great bank and boat access, especially near <strong>Lewis and Clark State Park</strong> and <strong>Dabney State Recreation Area</strong>.
</p>
<h3>
    Willamette River Zones
</h3>
<p>
